@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tvcgwc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.exp(v0 + 0.68) + (tmp + 0.27 + v1 + 0.49)))
    tmp = 0.74
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.18) - v0)
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.74 + v2 + 0.61) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.26)) - v0)
    v1 = (v1 * (tmp * 0.35))
    tmp = (v1 - wp.abs((v1 + 0.54 - v0 + 0.52)))
    tmp = wp.sin((v0 * (tmp + 0.40 / v1 + 0.79)))
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
